# ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Microsoft Excel Online (Graph API)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Setup:
#   1. Register an app in Microsoft Entra (Azure AD) admin center
#   2. Create a client secret under "Certificates & secrets"
#   3. Add Application permission: Files.ReadWrite.All → Grant admin consent
#   4. Create an Excel workbook on OneDrive/SharePoint with tables:
#      Contact, Career, Recruitment, CorporateTraining, FreshersDrive
#   5. Get the Drive ID and Workbook Item ID from Graph Explorer or URL
MS_GRAPH_TENANT_ID=your-azure-tenant-id
MS_GRAPH_CLIENT_ID=your-azure-client-id
MS_GRAPH_CLIENT_SECRET=your-azure-client-secret
MS_GRAPH_DRIVE_ID=your-onedrive-drive-id
MS_GRAPH_WORKBOOK_ITEM_ID=your-excel-file-item-id

